        <abstract> 
<p>Detailed questions about illustrations for [forthcoming] <hi rend="italic">Expression</hi>.</p>  
<p>Asks whether <hi rend="italic">Times</hi> review has hurt sales of <hi rend="italic">Descent</hi>.</p>  
<p>The type on specimen page of <hi rend="italic">Origin</hi> [6th ed.] seems clear, but lines are close. The cost is the great point for a wide circulation.</p> 
        </abstract>
